reviewText: Good movies at a bargain price!
Not a bad movie in the bunch
none

These are all good movies.  The Jekyll-Hyde story, haunted houses, unidentified bones, April Fool's pranks, stealing human organs, spooky stuff.  The only one I didn't really like was "The Nines."  I understood what they were doing but I didn't see why.  It left me confused about why I was watching it, and the ending didn't clear it up for me.

This is a good collection and a great bargain.
